metadata.description: Welcome To Krash World --- These 44 keys are the first points of access into the world that GRL lives in. Each key has a specific texture that corresponds to a terrain or creature in Krash World and will determine future access to experiences and parts of the world. These are the keys to our community and the world we will build together. This genesis run of digital collectibles will allow premium access to the next set of collectibles and keys. I want to give a big thanks to [Easy NFT](https://twitter.com/EasyNFT_) for this beautiful contract developed by [HalfSuperShop](https://www.halfsupershop.com/).
metadata.name: KRASH KEY
